### Dairy Innovation Hub Symposium 2023

Presentation given by **Dr. Tadeu Eder da Silva** and **Dr. Prof. Victor Cabrera** at the **Dairy Innovation Hub Symposium 2023**.  
In this session, we introduced and demonstrated the **DairyPrint model**, a decision-support model designed to evaluate dairy farm sustainability by integrating biological processes and simulating management strategies.
